body.name: HODAKOOK Wine Bar Cabinet with Led Lights Strip, Farmhouse Bar Cabinet for Liquor and Glasses, Industrial Coffee Bar Cabinet with Removable Wine Racks for Dining Room Kitchen (Gray)
features: Cool Smart Led Lights Wine Bar: This wine bar cabinet is a modern, industrial style, and adds LED lights for fun. The 7 main colors and 20 display modes can be chosen to match the atmosphere you’re trying to get for your home bar space.

Ample Storage Space: Mid-sized to fit almost anywhere but still ample storage for the average coffee bar collection. It easily holds 9 upside-down glasses on the middle display shelf. The right sides can accommodate more irregular bottles of wine, liquor mixers and cups.

Reliable Materials & Sturdy Structure: Constructed of high-grade MDF board and thickened steel frame, this coffee and wine bar is long-lasting that you can count on it to be a favorite for years to come. Sturdy bar cabinet that gives rustic farmhouse vibes, can be used as wine cabinet, coffee bar, console table, buffet cabinet or TV stand in living room ,dining room, kitchen or office space.

Freestanding Wine Cabinet & Versatile: Our wine cabinet has a detachable wine rack that can hold 12 bottles of red wine. As stylish as practical, it can not only be used as a wine rack table in the living room but also as a bar stand, coffee bar, console table, serving buffet, or storage sideboard in the dining room or kitchen.
Industrial-Chic Design: With an industrial vintage style design, equipped with the acrylic door, this wine bar cabinet will grace your home bar and perfectly blend into any style of home decor.

Easy to Assemble & Clean: All assembly hardware and tools come with the small liquor cabinet. With Illustrated instructions, this coffee bar cabinet can be assembled within 30 min without effort. Adjustable feet pads included ensure more stability and protecting your floor from scratches.
